title: Initial report: Israel Air Forces strikes Damascus overnight - Arab-Israeli Conflict - Jerusalem Post
text:
Initial report: Israel Air Forces strikes Damascus overnight By JPOST.COM STAFF February 22, 2017 07:49 Israel Air Force F-16s line up for takeoff at an air base in Israel. (photo credit:IDF) 
Reports claimed on Wednesday morning that the IDF struck targets in the Syrian capital overnight at least twice. The IDF Spokesperson's Unit declined to comment on the reports. Relevant to your professional network? Please share on Linkedin Be the first to know - Join our Facebook page. Tags:
